</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_320" id="159v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_320_r1l19"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_320_r1l20"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> . <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> / . Als vns <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> edel her <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>elt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> cʒü Plawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l21"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat vmb einen <expan>fruntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> tag cʒeſuchen dabeÿ er auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l22"> <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein wöll / 
<del rend="strikethrough">w </del> auf den Samſtag als <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> hewt <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> Acht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l23">das ıſt auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag <expan>Aſſu<ex>m</ex>pc<ex>ionis</ex></expan> / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_320_r1l17">cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Newenſt<ex>at</ex></expan> mıt </ab><ab facs="#facs_320_r1l18"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Steınpach </ab></add> vnd wir Jm <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l24"><expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / den tag alſo <expan>cʒeſüche<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo <expan>bıtt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir dıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l25"><expan>fleiʒʒiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ du <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> auf den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l26"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag reiten wölleſt / So wöllen wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l27">etwen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Rates vnd <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan> die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l28">dir ſchıcken / die mit dir cʒü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> tage <expan>reıt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l29"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / . vnd <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> die <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tıgen</expan> vnd Jn <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l31"><expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beuelhen / als ſie dir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_320_r1l30">fürbas </ab></add> wol ſagen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l32">werden / . vnd <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> dir wol du tüſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l33">das durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> dich daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l34">du vns bey <expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreibſt</expan> / wo dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_320_r1l35"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> alſo cʒü dir kumen ſüllen / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_320" id="159v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>, als uns <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> edel her
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> czü Plawen,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat umb einen
                                <expan>fruntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> tag cze suchen, dabey er auch
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> sein wöll auf den samstag als
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> hewt <expan>üb<ex>er</ex></expan> acht,
                        das ist <app><note><q type="date">auf <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag
                            <expan>assu<ex>m</ex>pc<ex>ionis</ex></expan></q>15.08.1411</note></app>, <add>czü
                                    <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Newenst<ex>at</ex></expan> mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                            Steinpach</add> und wir im <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, den tag also <expan>cze
                            süche<ex>n</ex></expan>, also <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir dich
                                <expan>fleizziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz du
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> auf den <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag
                        reiten wöllest. So wöllen wir etwen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> rates und
                                <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czü
                        dir schicken, die mit dir czü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> tage
                                <expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, und <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigen</expan> und in
                            <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> bevelhen, als sie dir <add>fürbas</add> wol
                        sagen werden. Und <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> dir wol, du tüst das
                        durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> dich, daz
                        du uns bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibst</expan>, wo die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        also czü dir kumen süllen.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
